dct_title_s: The State of New Jersey from original surveys based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Counties and townships outlined in red. Above top border: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet no. 18 (State Map).
